params._secsPerYear: secs in a year, default value = 31556952 * 1e18

params.liquidity: total balance of the underlying asset in the pool
params.totalDebt: balance of underlying assets borrowed from the pool

MAX_EXCESS_USAGE_RATIO().notice: This constant represents the excess usage ratio above the optimal. It's always equal to 1-optimal usage ratio.

OPTIMAL_USAGE_RATIO().notice: This constant represents the usage ratio at which the pool aims to obtain most competitive borrow rates

slope1().notice: Slope of the variable interest curve when usage ratio > 0 and <= OPTIMAL_USAGE_RATIO

slope2().notice: Slope of the variable interest curve when usage ratio > OPTIMAL_USAGE_RATIO
